comment_data.body:
To be it looks like you've got a compiled version of the `Code.py` module from an older version of Cython that is somehow being used in preference. 

I say that because the last line of your traceback doesn't really line up with the code in the source file.

I'm not sure how that happened or what you should do about it though, but that's what it looks like to me.
Still getting the same issue after uninstalling cython via pip and then trying to build it from Git
